<h1>PlateAgain</h1>

<h3>Connecting surplus food providers and organizations that can accept them for meal programs.</h3>


<div class="large-6 column">
  <h2>Food providers</h2>
  <p>Restaurants, caterers, and event planners: you can provide food to people who need it!</p>
  <p><%= link_to 'Learn more', about_providers_path %></p>
  <p><%= link_to 'See current providers', providers_path %></p>
  <p><%= link_to 'Sign up!', new_user_path %></p>
</div>


<div class="large-6 column">
  <h2>Food acceptors</h2>
  <p>If you run a meal program and need food, we can connect you with suppliers!</p>
  <p><%= link_to 'Learn more', about_acceptors_path %></p>
  <p><%= link_to 'See current acceptors', acceptors_path %></p>
  <p><%= link_to 'Sign up!', new_user_path %></p>
</div>
